  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pot over medium-high heat.",
    "Add chicken and cook until browned, about 5 minutes. Remove from pot and set aside.",
    "Add onion, bell pepper, and garlic to the pot and cook until tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add aji amarillo peppers and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Stir in tomato paste, cumin, paprika, salt, and pepper. Cook for 1 minute.",
